highlights.text: “Que Tire Pa Lante” by Daddy Yankee is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 46 spots at #65.
Post Malone has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Circles” is the highest at #5.
“Follow God” by Kanye West is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #4.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 147 weeks straight.
